(1055, 4, '2013-06-13 12:52:08', '2013-06-13 11:52:08', '<h2>Description</h2>\r\nPermet d''envoyer des messages entre les diff&eacute;rentes couches de l''application.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>messageNumber</strong> contient le num&eacute;ro (si possible unique) qui permettra de faciliter la traduction des messages dans d''autres langues</li>\r\n	<li><strong>message </strong>contient un string informant la couche sup&eacute;rieure de l''&eacute;tat atteint &agrave; ce stade</li>\r\n	<li><strong>status</strong> contient un bool&eacute;en, vrai ou faux selon si c''est un message d''erreur ou de notification de r&eacute;ussite.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>content</strong> (optionnel) peut contenir un objet &agrave; faire passer &agrave; la couche sup&eacute;rieure. Vaudra NULL si on ne passe aucun param&egrave;tre.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n$args = array(\r\n    ''messageNumber'' =&gt; 001,\r\n    ''message''       =&gt; ''User logged'',\r\n    ''status''        =&gt; true,\r\n    ''content''       =&gt; $anObject\r\n);\r\n$messageOK = new Message($args);\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Messages</h2>\r\n<table border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>messageNumber</td>\r\n<td>message</td>\r\n<td>status</td>\r\n<td>content</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>001</td>\r\n<td>User logged</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #339966;">true</span></td>\r\n<td> Member</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>002</td>\r\n<td>Login failure</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">false</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">null</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>003</td>\r\n<td>Wrong password</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">false</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">null</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>004</td>\r\n<td>Login or password is not a string</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">false</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">null</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>005</td>\r\n<td>Missing action argument</td>\r\n<td>