(1207, 1, '2013-06-13 14:20:58', '2013-06-13 13:20:58', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nService applicatif qui permet d’enregistrer un visiteur du site &agrave; un Event.\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n// Args RegisterToAnEvent\r\n$args = array(\r\n    ''person'' =&gt; $aPerson, // object Person\r\n    ''event'' =&gt; $anEvent, // object Event\r\n    ''slots'' =&gt; $aListOfSlots, // List of objects Slot\r\n    ''registrationdate'' =&gt; ''1991-04-26'', // Date\r\n    ''type'' =&gt; ''Presse'', // String\r\n    ''typedescription'' =&gt; ''Redacteur chez Edipresse SA'' // String\r\n);\r\n// Register to an Event\r\n$aRegisteredParticipant = ASVisitor::registerToAnEvent( $args );\r\n\r\n// Message\r\nif( $aRegisteredParticipant-&gt;getStatus() == 1 )\r\n    echo ''Congrats! '' . $aRegisteredParticipant-&gt;getMessage();\r\nelse\r\n    echo ''Error! '' . $aRegisteredParticipant-&gt;getMessage();\r\n\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\n[code language="html"]\r\nCongrats! Registered to an event\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Param&egrave;tre</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n$args = array(\r\n    ''person'' =&gt; '''', // object Person\r\n    ''event'' =&gt; '''', // object Event\r\n    ''slots'' =&gt; '''', // List of objects Slot\r\n    ''registrationdate'' =&gt; '''', // Date\r\n    ''type'' =&gt; '''', // String\r\n    ''typedescription'' =&gt; '''' // String\r\n);\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Valeurs de retour</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>aRegisteredParticipant</strong>, un message qui dit si l''enregistrement c''est bien pass&eacute;<span style="line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;">.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\r\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\r\n\r\n<strong>/core/services/applicatives/ASVisitor.class.php</strong>\r\n<h2>Mod&eacute;lisation des traitements</h2>\r\n<a href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MIT40_SA:registerToAnEvent_v1.0.pdf">MIT40_SA_registerToAnEvent_v