rviceAccess.class.php</strong></em>\n\n<strong>Articles en relations</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Service Person\n<ul>\n	<li>Service Keyword</li>\n	<li>Service Member</li>\n	<li>Service Unit</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'Service fonctionnel Access', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '364-revision-11', '', '', '2013-06-14 17:08:47', '2013-06-14 16:08:47', '', 364, 'http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/364-revision-11', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1333, 1, '2013-06-14 16:48:56', '2013-06-14 15:48:56', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nLe service Event est une class ne poss&eacute;dant que des m&eacute;thodes statique permettant l''insertion, la modification, l''archivage et la recherche d''Events.\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n//access to the main controller\r\nrequire_once(''tedx-config.php'');\r\n\r\n// get Event with no 1\r\n$anEvent = ServiceEvent::getEvent(1);\r\n\r\n// Display the main topic\r\necho ''Main topic : ''. $anEvent-&gt;getMainTopic() ;\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\n[code language="html"]\r\n&lt;code&gt;Main topic : T&eacute;l&eacute;phonie mobile&lt;/code&gt;\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>M&eacute;thodes</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode getEvent()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-getevent">static getEvent()</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode getEvents()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-getevents">static getEvents()</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode addEvent()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-addevent">static addEvent()</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode setEvent()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-setevent">static setEvent()</a> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>- Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode archiveEvent()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-archiveevent">static archiveEvent()</a> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>- Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li>static searchEvents() <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>- Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\r\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>/core/Services/ServiceEvent.class.php</strong></em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Articles en relations</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Location</li>\r\n	<li>Service Slot</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n