(799, 3, '2013-06-11 13:59:39', '2013-06-11 12:59:39', '<h2>Description</h2>\r\nPermet d''envoyer des messages entre les diff&eacute;rentes couches de l''application.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>messageNumber</strong> contient le num&eacute;ro unique du message</li>\r\n	<li><strong>message</strong> contient une description longue du message</li>\r\n	<li><strong>status</strong> contient un bool&eacute;en, vrai ou faux selon si c''est un message d''erreur ou de notification de r&eacute;ussite.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n<h2>Messages</h2>\r\n<table border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>messageNumber</td>\r\n<td>message</td>\r\n<td>status</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>001</td>\r\n<td>User logged</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #339966;">true</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>002</td>\r\n<td>Login failure</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">false</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>003</td>\r\n<td>Wrong password</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">false</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2>M&eacute;thodes</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="line-height: 14px;">__construct(arrayOfArguments)</span></li>\r\n	<li>public getMessageNumber()</li>\r\n	<li>public getMessage()</li>\r\n	<li>public getStatus()</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Class Message', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '785-revision-5', '', '', '2013-06-11 13:59:39', '2013-06-11 12:59:39', '', 785, 'http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/785-revision-5', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(800, 3, '2013-06-11 14:21:16', '2013-06-11 13:21:16', '<h2>Description</h2>\r\nPermet d''envoyer des messages entre les diff&eacute;rentes couches de l''application.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>messageNumber</strong> contient le num&eacute;ro unique du message</li>\r\n	<li><strong>message</strong> contient une description longue du message</li>\r\n	<li><strong>status</strong> contient un bool&eacute;en, vrai ou faux selon si c''est un message d''erreur ou de notification de r&eacute;ussite.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n$args = array(\r\n    ''messageNumber'' =&amp;gt; 001,\r\n    ''message''       =&amp;gt; ''User logged'',\r\n    ''status''        =&amp;gt; true\r\n);\r\n$messageOK = new Message($args);\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Messages</h2>\r\n<table border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>messageNumber</td>\r\n<td>message</td>\r\n<td>status</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>001</td>\r\n<td>User logged</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #339966;">true</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>002</td>\r\n<td>Login failure</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">false</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>003</td>\r\n<td>Wrong password</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">false</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>004</td>\r\n<td>Login or password is not a string</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #ff0000;">false</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2>M&eacute;thodes</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="line-height: 14px;">__construct(arrayOfArguments)</span></li>\r\n	<li>public getMessageNumber()</li>\r\n	<li>public getMessage()</li>\r\n	<li>public getStatus()</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Class Message', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '785-revision-6', '', '', '2013-06-11 14:21:16', '2013-06-11 13:21:16', '', 785, 'http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/785-revision-6', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(801, 6, '2013-06-11 14:11:14', '2013-06-11 13:11:14', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nService applicatif qui permet d’enregistrer un visiteur du site avec les acc&egrave;s participants.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 1.285714286rem; line-height: 1.6;">Usage</span>\r\n\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n// Args Role\r\n$args = array(\r\n    ''name''     =&gt; ''vendeur de merguez'' // String\r\n    ''slot''     =&gt; $anEvent,   // object Event\r\n    ''speaker''  =&gt; $anOrganizer // object Organizer\r\n    ''level''    =&gt; 1 // int\r\n);\r\n// Adding the Role\r\n$RoleAdded = ServiceRole::addRole( $args );\r\n\r\n// Message\r\nif( isset( $roleAdded ) )\r\n    echo ''Role added successfully'';\r\nelse\r\n    echo ''error while adding the Role'';\r\n\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\n[code language="html"]\r\nRole added successfully\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Param&egrave;tre</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n$args = array(\r\n    ''name''     =&gt; '''',   // String\r\n    ''event''     =&gt; '''',   // object Event\r\n    ''organizer''  =&gt; ''''    // object Organizer\r\n    ''level'' =&gt; 0  // Int\r\n);\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Valeurs de retour</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>L''objet <a title="Class Role" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-role">Role</a> ins&eacute;r&eacute; dans la base.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nou\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>null </strong>si l''objet n''a pas pu ecirc;tre ins&eacute;r&eacute;.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\r\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\r\n\r\n<strong>/core/Services/Service_Role.class.php</strong>\r\n<h2>Mod&eacute;lisation des traitements</h2>\r\n<a href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MIT40_addRole_v3.0.pdf">MIT40_addRole_v3.0</a>', 'M&eacute;thode registerVisitor()', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '794-revision-2', '', '', '2013-06-11 14:11:14', '2013-06-11 13:11:14', '', 794, 'http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/794-revision-2', 0, 'revision