(972, 3, '2013-06-13 09:09:22', '2013-06-13 08:09:22', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nLe service Auth est une classe <em></em>m&eacute;tier permettant de g&eacute;rer les acc&egrave;s des membres, et de se loguer &agrave; l''application.\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n//access to the main controler\r\nrequire_once(''tedx-config.php'');\r\n\r\n// get the authentication status, or if the user is logged\r\n$isLogged = ASAuth::isLogged();\r\n\r\nif($isLogged){\r\n    // Display a welcome message\r\n    echo ''You are logged as''. $auth-&gt;getUsername().'', how are you today ?'' ;\r\n}\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\n[code language="html"]\r\nYou are logged as VaterGrune69, how are you today ?\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>M&eacute;thodes</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>isGranted()</li>\r\n	<li>isLogged()<strong>\r\n</strong></li>\r\n	<li>getUsername() <strong>- Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</strong></li>\r\n	<li>login( array( username, password ) )</li>\r\n	<li>logout()</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\r\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>/core/services/applicatives/ASAuth.class.php</strong></em>', 'Service Auth', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '287-revision-6', '', '', '2013-06-13 09:09:22', '2013-06-13 08:09:22', '', 287, 'http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/287-revision-6', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
